                                 <h2 class="title">Climate Connection</h2>
                                 <div class="content">
                                    <ul>
                                       <li class="ts-386x217 first i-w386 i-h217 teaser">
                                          <h3 class="link title"><a href="/web/20101203185840/http://www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/science/2010/12/101203_climate_connection_prog_five_tx.shtml"
                                                class="audio">What's Stopping Us?<img alt="A flooded house in Poland. Reuters" width="386" height="217"
                                                     src="/web/20101203185840im_/http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/11/29/101129224538_poland_flood_climate_reuters_386x217_nocredit.jpg" /></a></h3>
                                          <p class="summary">If so many people across the globe accept climate change is happening, why aren't we taking more action to tackle it? Is it something to do with how we think, our culture, money or the lack of leadership?</p>
                                          <p class="cta"><a href="/web/20101203185840/http://www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/science/2010/12/101203_climate_connection_prog_five_tx.shtml"
